# 📊 Hotel Revenue & Booking Performance Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes hotel booking data to uncover insights into revenue performance, customer behavior, and cancellation trends.

The analysis was conducted using:
- Excel (Data Cleaning & Preparation)
- SQL (Data Analysis)
- Power BI (Dashboard & Visualization)

---

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze booking trends over time
- Identify top revenue-generating segments
- Evaluate cancellation patterns
- Provide business insights for decision-making

---

## 📊 Key Metrics
- Total Bookings: 500
- Total Revenue: $417,000
- Average ADR: $175
- Cancellation Rate: 32%

---

## 🔍 Key Insights
- January recorded the highest revenue, indicating strong start-of-year demand.
- Corporate segment generated the highest revenue with relatively lower cancellation risk.
- Weekday bookings are higher than weekends, suggesting business travel demand.
- Online segment shows the highest cancellation rate, indicating potential revenue leakage.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Excel (Power Query)
- SQL (PostgreSQL)
- Power BI

---

